.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

The people have 5 different hobbies: hiking, reading, drawing, singing, collecting
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, zinnia, amaryllis, iris
City: boston, venice, colone, prague, miami
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, d&b, hip-hop, electronic, classical
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, may, august, february, december
1. the person who growsazalea is the person who's hobby is drawing
2. the person who growsswedish is the person who's birthday is in august
3. the person who growslily is the person traveling to prague
4. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing
5. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to venice
6. the fan of hip-hop is the person who's birthday is in may
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of d&b
8. the person traveling to colone is in the middle
9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left
10. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june
11. the person who's birthday is in decembers is on the left or right of the fan of d&b
12. the fan of house is the person traveling to boston
13. the person who growszinnia is the fan of electronic
14. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking
15. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person traveling to miami

.:: Answer ::.
